HEADWORD: Stenodermine
<hw>Sten`o*der"mine</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>Of or pertaining to the genus <gen>Stenoderma</gen>, which includes
several West Indian and South American nose-leaf bats.</def>⟦br⟧
